# Environment Variables Template

Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your values.

## Deepgram Voice Agent (Cartivo Voice™)

```env
# Deepgram API key — Get from: https://console.deepgram.com
# Requires Voice Agent API access
VITE_DEEPGRAM_API_KEY=YOUR_DEEPGRAM_API_KEY
```

---

## Sanity Configuration

```env
# Sanity Project ID - Get from: https://manage.sanity.io
SANITY_PROJECT_ID=YOUR_PROJECT_ID

# Sanity Dataset (default: production)
SANITY_DATASET=production
```

## Foxit PDF APIs (PDF Report Generator)

```env
# Foxit API key - Get from: https://developers.foxit.com
# Used by both Document Generation API and PDF Services API
VITE_FOXIT_API_KEY=YOUR_FOXIT_API_KEY

# Foxit Document Generation API base URL (optional override)
VITE_FOXIT_DOC_GEN_URL=https://api.foxitsoftware.com/document-generation/v1

# Foxit PDF Services API base URL (optional override)
VITE_FOXIT_PDF_SERVICES_URL=https://api.foxitsoftware.com/pdf-services/v1

# Foxit template ID for the Cartivo bundle report (pre-configured in Foxit dashboard)
VITE_FOXIT_TEMPLATE_ID=cartivo-smart-bundle-report-v1

# Your app's public URL (used for QR code share links)
VITE_APP_URL=http://localhost:5173
```

Without `VITE_FOXIT_API_KEY`, the PDF Report Generator runs in **demo mode**:
it generates an HTML report instead, which you can print to PDF via the browser.

## Kendo License (Optional but recommended for production)

```env
VITE_KENDO_LICENSE_KEY=YOUR_LICENSE_KEY
```

Get your Kendo license from: https://www.telerik.com/kendo-react-ui

